<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.4.7">
<l>villēr nutalār vēṭkaiyai māṟṟici rittivaṉ</l>
<l>pollāṉ tiraintā ṉeṉṉumpuṟa ṉuraikēṭ pataṉmuṉ</l>
<l>collār maṟaināṉ kōtiyu lakilni lāyavar</l>
<l>nallār naṟaiyūr nāmtoḻu tumeḻu neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before [I] hear the slanderous words, “He’s horrid and wrinkled!”</l>
<l>Which those with bow-like foreheads say,</l>
<l rend="indent">tittering [and] altering [their] affections,</l>
<l>Arise, [my] heart! We will worship in Naṟaiyūr with noble people,</l>
<l>Those who, chanting the four praise-filled Vedas, shine in the world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
